"Your privacy, protected",privacy_desc:"Your and your partner's data stays on your device. We don't upload it to our servers; everything is processed locally.",storage_title:"Your data, your device",storage_desc:"Choose a place to keep the memories you share with your loved one.",storage_desc_mobile:"BaiShou must store diaries and summaries in the fixed BaiShou_Root folder (/storage/emulated/0/BaiShou_Root, same as desktop) so you can manage them in any file manager. Grant “All files access” before saving—no sandbox fallback.",storage_subtitle_mobile:"Required: all files access",current_storage:"Current Storage:",select_storage:"Select Path",change_storage:"Change Path",storage_permission_error:"Cannot access selected directory, please ensure read/write permissions.",get_started:"Start Journey",skip:"Skip",config_now:"Configure Now",later:"Maybe Later",daily_report:"Daily",weekly_report:"Weekly",monthly_report:"Monthly",quarterly_report:"Quarterly",yearbook:"Yearbook",welcome:"Welcome to BaiShou",welcome_sub:"Setting up your personal workspace and initializing index configuration.",start:"Start Journey",ai_config_title:"Configure AI Services",ai_config_desc:"BaiShou doesn't store your keys. Configure an AI provider to chat with your companion and generate memory summaries. Go to Settings > Provider Management when ready—or set this up later.",ai_config_hint:"Hint",ai_config_steps:"Go to Settings > Provider Management when ready—or set this up later.",import_title:"Import Data",import_desc:'If you have previous backup data, you can import it through the "Data Management" feature in settings after completing the guide.',import_hint:"Hint",import_steps:"After completing the guide, please go to: Settings → Data Management → Import Backup, select your ZIP backup file to restore data.",slogan:'"Pure White Vow, Guarding a Lifetime"'},settings:JSON.parse(`{"tooltip_summary_model":"This model is used to generate weekly, monthly, quarterly summaries and annuals. Choosing a hi