a to migrate.","rag_migration_detecting_dimension":"Detecting new model dimension...","rag_migration_dimension_failed":"Failed to detect the new model dimension. Migration aborted.","rag_migration_reembedding":"Re-embedding memories...","rag_migration_in_progress":"{{completed}}/{{total}} re-embedded","rag_migration_in_progress_with_failures":"{{completed}}/{{total}} re-embedded ({{failed}} failed)","rag_migration_complete_status":"Migration complete ✅ {{completed}}/{{total}}","rag_migration_verify_partial":"Migration finished with warnings ⚠️ Some chunks were not migrated ({{completed}}/{{total}}).","rag_migration_verify_stale":"Migration finished with warnings ⚠️ Stale model data remains ({{completed}}/{{total}}).","rag_migration_verify_both":"Migration finished with warnings ⚠️ Some chunks were not migrated and stale data remains ({{completed}}/{{total}}).","rag_migration_finished":"Migration finished.","rag_migration_aborting":"Migration failed. Restoring previous embeddings and model settings...","rag_migration_aborted_consecutive":"Migration stopped after {{limit}} consecutive failures. Previous data and embedding model have been restored.","rag_migration_cancelled":"Migration cancelled. Previous data and embedding model have been restored.","rag_migration_backup_lost":"Migration backup table is missing. Start a new embedding migration; if a rollback snapshot exists, try Restore migration backup in settings.","rag_migration_cancel":"Cancel migration","rag_migration_cancel_confirm":"Cancel migration and restore the previous vector data and embedding model?","rag_migration_aborted_restored":"Migration aborted. Previous vector data and embedding model settings have been restored.","rag_migration_interrupted_title":"Incomplete embedding migration detected","rag_migration_interrupted_restore_desc":"Migration did not finish. A full pre-migration backup is available — you can restore your previous vectors and embedding model in one click.","rag_migration_interrupted_