p below to finish embedding.","rag_operation_failed":"Embedding operation failed","rag_batch_embed_concurrency":"Batch embed concurrency","rag_batch_embed_concurrency_hint":"How many diaries to embed in parallel. Higher is faster but more likely to hit API rate limits; 2–3 is recommended.","rag_add_manual":"Add Snapshot","rag_add_manual_success":"Memory fragment added","rag_add_manual_failed":"Failed to add: ","rag_empty_desc":"When the AI reads diaries or generates thoughts, vector embeddings will be persisted and managed here.","rag_edit_prompt":"Edit the memory fragment below:","rag_edit_manual":"Edit memory","rag_search_semantic_hint":"Semantic search memory...","rag_search_text_hint":"Text search memory...","rag_search_semantic":"Semantic Search","rag_search_text":"Text Search","rag_semantic_unavailable_title":"Semantic search requires RAG setup","rag_semantic_unavailable_message":"Enable RAG memory and configure an embedding model to use semantic search. Go to settings?","rag_go_configure":"Configure","rag_pagination_info":"$total items","rag_per_page":"/ page","rag_jump_to_page":"Jump","rag_export":"Export Data","rag_manage_backups":"Manage Backups","rag_export_success":"Export successful","rag_export_empty":"No data to export","rag_export_error":"Export failed: ","rag_entries":"items","rag_no_backups":"No backups available","rag_backup_list":"Available backups:","rag_backup_actions":"Enter number to restore, or \\"delete:number\\" to delete:","rag_confirm_delete_backup":"Delete this backup?","rag_backup_deleted":"Backup deleted","rag_confirm_restore":"Restore will clear current memories and import from backup. Continue?","rag_restore_success":"Restore successful","rag_backup_error":"Operation failed: ","rag_total_count":"Total:","rag_vault_diary_count":"{{vault}} diary vectors","rag_model":"Model:","rag_dimension":"Dimension:","rag_top_k":"Top-K Recall Limit","rag_top_k_tooltip":"Maximum number of most similar memories returned when AI searches. Higher value