cks all diaries and settings into a zip backup. Renaming a backup file marks it as 'Manual'. When the backup limit is exceeded and auto-cleanup triggers, only normal backups will be deleted, ensuring 'Manual' records are safely preserved.","snapshot_tooltip":"Local snapshots are historical backups automatically generated by the system. To avoid redundancy, they are only created in two scenarios: 1. before restoring a full backup; 2. before restoring/applying a local snapshot. Restoring a snapshot will revert all data, settings, and database states to the exact moment the snapshot was created.","incremental_sync_tooltip":"Two-way incremental sync scans all vaults: diaries, summaries, chat sessions, AI partners, attachments, and \`.baishou/settings/\` (including API config). Only changed files are transferred, and deletions propagate. Default cloud prefix is memories_sync, separate from full backup.","incremental_sync_scope_all_vaults":"All vaults","incremental_sync_enable_warning_title":"Enable file sync?","incremental_sync_enable_warning":"Sync keeps the version with the latest file modification time and overwrites the older copy on the other side. This can cause unexpected data loss. Please make sure you understand the risk.\\n\\nAPI keys and other sensitive settings in each vault's \`.baishou/settings/\` will also be synced to the cloud. Ensure your cloud storage access is properly secured.\\n\\nWe recommend enabling version control (Git) on desktop to protect your data. Mobile is better suited for one-way backup.","incremental_sync_scope_title":"Sync scope","incremental_sync_scope_diary":"Diaries","incremental_sync_scope_summary":"Summaries","incremental_sync_scope_sessions":"Chat sessions","incremental_sync_scope_partners":"AI partners","incremental_sync_scope_attachments":"Attachments (including avatars)","incremental_sync_scope_settings":"Each vault's \`.baishou/settings/\` (including API config)","incremental_sync_scope_registry":"Vault registry (vault_registry.json)","backup_scope_title":"Full backup scope","backup_scope_intro":"Packages data into a ZIP archive (not bidirectional incremental file sync)","backup_scope_root":"Full vault file tree under workspace root (diaries, summaries, sessions, AI partners, attachments, per-vault settings, etc.)","backup_scope_database":"SQLite database (baishou_agent.db)","backup_scope_database_detail":"Includes Agent sessions and messages, AI partner config, summary index, and RAG vector memories","backup_scope_device_prefs":"Device preferences (config/device_preferences.json)","backup_scope_not_incremental":"Unlike File Sync: full backup is a full overwrite restore; file sync incrementally syncs all vaults file-by-file","backup_scope_excludes_heading":"Not included (rebuilt after import or kept locally)","backup_scope_excludes_shadow":"Diary full-text search index (Shadow index, rebuilt automatically after import)","backup_scope_excludes_sync_meta":"Incremental sync state (manifest, ancestor snapshot, etc., reset after import)","backup_scope_import_note":"Import fully overwrites data; cloud sync settings (cloud_sync_config) keep current local values, all other data comes from the backup","cloud_restore_warning":"Restore will fully overwrite workspace and database (cloud sync settings kept locally). Continue?","confirm_cloud_restore":"Confirm restore","delete_record_warning":"Delete cloud backup \\"{{name}}\\"?","confirm_delete_record":"Confirm delete","record_deleted":"Backup record deleted","delete_record_failed":"Delete failed","batch_delete_warning":"Delete {{count}} selected backups?","confirm_batch_delete":"Confirm batch delete","batch_deleted":"Deleted {{count}} backups","batch_delete_failed":"Batch delete failed","name_required":"Please enter a new filename","record_renamed":"Renamed successfully","rename_failed":"Rename failed","load_records_failed":"Failed to load backup records","new_name_placeholder":"Enter new filename","desc":"Sync your memories to cloud (S3 or WebDAV) for multi-device backup.","sync_target":"Sync Target","target_local":"Local Only","target_local_desc":"Stored only on this device, no cloud sync","target_s3":"S3 Storage","target_s3_desc":"MinIO, Cloudflare R2, Alibaba Cloud OSS, etc.","target_webdav":"WebDAV","target_webdav_desc":"Nextcloud, Synology, etc.","sync_stats":"Sync Stats","last_sync":"Last Sync","file_count":"Cloud Files","storage_used":"Storage Used","sync_records":"Cloud Backups","no_records":"No cloud backups found","cloud_backups_tab":"Cloud Backups","local_backup_tab":"Local Backup","local_snapshots_tab":"Local Snapshots","local_snapshots":"Local Snapshots","snapshots_scope_hint":"Local snapshots are automatically generated before major changes like restoring backups to facilitate data rollback.","no_snapshots_hint":"No local snapshots available","no_records_hint":"No sync records","local_target_no_cloud_records_desc":"You can switch to the \\"Local Snapshots\\" tab to manage system snapshots, or bind S3/WebDAV cloud storage in \\"Backup Settings\\".","local_target_no_cloud_records":"Current backup target is local storage.","loading_snapshots":"Loading local snapshots...","max_snapshot_title":"Snapshot Limit Settings","max_snapshot_desc":"Once the limit is exceeded, the oldest snapshots will be automatically cleaned when new snapshots are generated.","count_unit_value":"$count","fetching_records":"Fetching records...","backup_now":"Backup Now (Manual)","backup_success":"Backup saved","backup_failed":"Backup failed","restore_confirm_title":"Confirm Restore","restore_confirm_desc":"Restoring will overwrite all local data. Continue?","import_success":"Restore successful. Reloading app...","rename_title":"Rename Backup","new_filename":"New Filename","delete_confirm_title":"Delete Backup","delete_confirm_desc":"Are you sure you want to permanently delete this backup?","config_title":"Data Sync Config","s3_endpoint":"Endpoint","s3_bucket":"Bucket","s3_access_key":"Access Key","s3_secret_key":"Secret Key","s3_region":"Region (Optional)","webdav_url":"Server URL","webdav_user":"Username","webdav_password":"Password/App Token","test_connection":"Test Connection","testing":"Testing...","test_success":"Connection successful","test_failed":"Connection failed: {{e}}","save_config":"Save Config","placeholder_endpoint":"e.g., s3.example.com","placeholder_bucket":"Bucket name","placeholder_webdav":"e.g., https://dav.box.com/dav","error_empty":"Please fill in all required fields","error_url":"Please enter a valid URL","backup_file_label":"Backup: $name","list_s3_failed":"Failed to list S3 backups: $e","list_webdav_failed":"Failed to list WebDAV files: $e","rename_webdav_failed":"Failed to rename WebDAV file: $e","size_mb":"Size: $size MB","restore_this_backup":"Restore this backup","restore_this":"Restore","rename":"Rename","delete":"Delete","fetch_records_failed":"Fetching records failed: $e","local_backup_hint":"Local backups don't need sync on this page","sync_success":"Sync successful!","sync_failed":"Sync failed: $e","total_backup_size":"Total Backup Size","total_snapshot_size":"Total Snapshot Size","backup_count":"Backup Count","snapshot_count":"Snapshot Count","backup_count_unit":"$count","records_scope_hint":"Records below only belong to current target","sync_settings_button":"Sync Settings","syncing_status":"Syncing...","sync_now_button":"Sync Now","delete_backup_title":"Delete Backup?","delete_backup_confirm":"Delete $name? This action is irreversible.","restore_backup_title":"Restore Backup?","restore_backup_confirm":"Warning: Restoring will overwrite all current data! Recommended to backup before restore.","start_restore_button":"Start Restore","select_target_title":"Select Sync Target","local_storage":"Local Storage","local_storage_desc":"Backup to local device directory","s3_storage":"S3 Cloud Storage","s3_storage_desc":"S3-compatible object storage services","webdav_storage":"WebDAV","webdav_storage_desc":"Generic network file protocol","local_no_config":"Local storage needs no extra config. Save to apply.","set_local_target":"Set Local as Target","s3_config_title":"S3 Config","webdav_config_title":"WebDAV Config","save_config_button":"Save Config","config_saved":"Configuration saved","new_filename_label":"New Filename","backup_filename_hint":"baishou_backup_xxx.zip","s3_endpoint_label":"Endpoint URL","s3_region_label":"Region","s3_bucket_label":"Bucket Name","s3_path_label":"Sub-path","s3_ak_label":"Access Key (AK)","s3_sk_label":"Secret Key (SK)","webdav_url_label":"Server URL","webdav_path_label":"Sub-path","webdav_user_label":"Username","webdav_password_label":"Password","max_backup_title":"Backup Limit","max_backup_desc":"Old backups will be auto-deleted when exceeding the limit","max_backup_count_label":"Max Backup Count","max_backup_count_value":"$count","max_backup_auto_cleaned":"Auto-cleaned $count old backup(s)","download_backup":"Download to Local","downloading":"Downloading...","download_success":"Saved to: $path","no_limit":"No Limit","loading_records":"Connecting to fetch cloud records...","batch_manage":"Batch Manage","name_url_required":"Name and URL cannot be empty","target_added":"Sync target added","add_failed":"Failed to add","delete_confirm":"Are you sure you want to delete this sync target?","confirm_restore":"Confirm Restore","restore_warning":"Restoring will overwrite current data. Continue?","restore_success":"Restore successful","restore_failed":"Restore failed","idle":"Idle","quick_actions":"Quick Actions","backup":"Backup Data","restore":"Restore Data","add_target":"Add Sync Target","target_name_placeholder":"Sync target name","username_placeholder":"Username (optional)","password_placeholder":"Password (optional)","targets":"Sync Targets","no_targets":"No sync targets","add_hint":"Click the add button in the top right to configure sync targets","sync_now":"Sync","incremental_sync":"Incremental Sync","incremental_sync_desc":"Scans all vaults under the storage root for two-way file sync with deletion propagation. For daily cross-device sync. Use Data Backup for full archives.","sync_mode_comparison_title":"File sync vs full backup","sync_mode_comparison_row_incremental":"Incremental file sync","sync_mode_comparison_row_full":"Full backup","sync_mode_comparison_incremental_desc":"Bidirectional per-file sync for all vaults; excludes the SQLite database; default cloud prefix memories_sync","sync_mode_comparison_full_desc":"ZIP archive overwrite restore; includes database and device preferences; use the Data Backup page","sync_mode_comparison_hint":"Different cloud paths and data scopes — do not mix the two.","sync_mode_comparison_help_aria":"Learn the difference between file sync and full backup","sync_completed":"Sync Completed","sync_result_summary":"$count files changed in $duration","sync_result_uploaded":"$count uploaded","sync_result_downloaded":"$count downloaded","sync_result_deleted":"$count deleted","sync_result_skipped":"$count skipped","sync_result_conflicts":"$count file conflicts auto-resolved","sync_actions":"Sync Actions","sync_failed_generic":"Sync failed","sync_unknown_error":"Unknown error","stat_uploaded":"Uploaded","stat_downloaded":"Downloaded","stat_deleted":"Deleted","stat_conflicts":"Auto-resolved","stat_skipped":"Skipped","stat_duration":"Duration","syncing":"Syncing...","planning":"Analyzing sync changes…","sync_retrying":"Sync request timed out, retrying ({{attempt}}/{{max}})…","sync_timeout_failed":"Sync request timed out after {{max}} retries. Please check your network and try again.","planning_blocking_hint":"Analyzing sync changes. Please stay on this screen.","sync_blocking_hint":"Sync in progress. Please stay on this screen.","sync_in_progress_leave_blocked":"Sync in progress. Please wait until it finishes.","plan_cancelled":"Sync analysis cancelled","sync_cancelled":"Sync cancelled","plan_warning_pruned_registry_vaults":"Removed from registry (no data on disk or cloud): {{vaults}}","plan_up_to_date":"Local and remote are already in sync","plan_confirm_title":"Confirm sync","plan_confirm_desc":"Active vault: {{activeVault}}. {{count}} file(s) will change across all vaults. Review and confirm to continue.","plan_confirm_sync":"Confirm sync","plan_confirm_sync_countdown":"Confirm sync ({{seconds}})","plan_confirm_button_countdown":"Confirm in {{seconds}}s","plan_confirm_countdown":"Review the list carefully. Confirm available in {{seconds}}s","plan_confirming":"Confirming…","plan_changed_reconfirm":"The sync plan changed. Review the updated list and confirm again.","plan_no_file_changes":"No file changes to sync","plan_active_vault":"active","plan_unregistered_vault":"unregistered","plan_auto_registered_vaults":"Auto-registered vaults: {{vaults}}","plan_vault_root":"Root files","plan_vault_unknown":"Unknown vault","plan_more_files":"{{count}} more file(s) not shown — tap to expand","plan_show_less":"Show fewer files","plan_stat_upload":"upload {{count}}","plan_stat_download":"download {{count}}","plan_stat_delete_local":"delete local {{count}}","plan_stat_delete_remote":"delete remote {{count}}","plan_stat_conflict":"conflict {{count}}","plan_boundary_disk_only":"On disk but not in registry","plan_boundary_registry_only":"In registry but missing on disk","plan_warning_unknown_vault_paths":"These vaults have file changes but are not in your local registry: {{paths}}. Create matching vaults in Settings → Workspaces, or confirm these folders should sync.","plan_warning_disk_vaults_not_in_registry":"Vault folders on disk are not in the registry: {{vaults}}. Sync will still process files in those folders.","plan_warning_registry_vaults_missing_on_disk":"These registered vaults are missing on disk: {{missing}}","plan_warning_high_divergence":"Large divergence from remote ({{divergence}}%, limit {{limit}}%). Continuing may overwrite many files.","plan_warning_delete_blocked":"Mass deletion or possible cloud/local data loss detected. Choose how to proceed — uploads and deletes will not run automatically.","plan_delete_choice_title_remote_loss":"Cloud has far fewer files","plan_delete_choice_title_local_loss":"Local has far fewer files","plan_delete_choice_title_mass_delete":"Confirm mass deletion","plan_delete_choice_desc_remote_loss":"The cloud has many fewer files than your last sync (cleared or bulk-deleted elsewhere). Choose: match cloud by deleting local copies, restore cloud from this device, or sync non-delete changes only.","plan_delete_choice_desc_local_loss":"This device has far fewer files than your last sync (possible local data loss). Choose: push local state to cloud, keep cloud files, or sync non-delete changes only.","plan_delete_choice_desc_mass_delete":"This sync would delete many files. Confirm whether this is intentional, then choose how to proceed.","plan_delete_choice_follow_remote":"Match cloud (delete local extras)","plan_delete_choice_push_local":"Use this device (upload / restore cloud)","plan_delete_choice_skip_deletes":"Sync other changes only","plan_delete_choice_blocked_count":"About {{count}} files involved in delete conflict","plan_warning_interrupted_session":"Last sync stopped at {{completed}}/{{total}}. Confirm to resume remaining items.","plan_action_upload":"upload","plan_action_download":"download","plan_action_delete_local":"del local","plan_action_delete_remote":"del remote","plan_action_conflict_resolved":"conflict","progress_upload":"Upload: {{path}}","progress_download":"Download: {{path}}","progress_delete":"Delete: {{path}}","progress_skip":"Skip: {{path}}","progress_scanning_local":"Scanning local files…","progress_fetching_remote":"Fetching remote manifest…","progress_git_commit":"Saving local Git snapshot…","progress_registering_vaults":"Preparing workspaces…","progress_finalizing":"Saving sync state…","config_section":"Configuration","target_type":"Target Type","path_prefix":"Path Prefix","file_concurrency":"File Concurrency","file_concurrency_option":"{{count}} files in parallel","chunk_concurrency":"Chunk Concurrency (large object storage)","max_divergence_label":"Max local/remote difference (bidirectional sync)","max_divergence_option":"{{percent}}%","max_divergence_remove_protection":"100 (remove protection)","max_divergence_hint":"Blocks bidirectional sync when local and remote manifests differ by more than this ratio. 100 disables this protection. S3 and WebDAV keep separate sync snapshots.","error_divergence_exceeded":"Local/remote divergence is {{divergence}}%, which exceeds your limit of {{limit}}%. Sync was aborted. Raise the limit or verify the correct storage target.","error_divergence_exceeded_generic":"Local and remote differ too much for the configured limit. Sync was aborted.","error_divergence_first_sync_confirm_title":"Confirm first sync","error_divergence_first_sync_confirm_message":"This device is connecting to this cloud target for the first time. Local/remote divergence is {{divergence}}%, above your limit of {{limit}}%. Continue only if this is the correct storage (e.g. restoring from another device). Otherwise cancel and check your settings.","error_delete_propagation_mass_delete":"This sync would delete a large number of remote files and was aborted. Choose how to handle deletions in the confirm dialog, or verify your local copy is complete.","error_delete_propagation_local_data_loss":"Local files are far fewer than the last sync record, suggesting local data loss. Bidirectional sync was blocked to protect remote data. Check your local data or restore from backup first.","chunk_concurrency_option":"{{count}} chunks in parallel","save_failed":"Save failed","testing_connection":"Testing connection...","connection_success":"Connection successful","connection_failed_check":"Connection failed, please check your configuration","connection_failed":"Connection failed","error_in_progress":"Sync is already in progress. Please wait.","error_not_initialized":"Sync service is not initialized. Please save your connection settings first.","error_not_configured":"Sync is not enabled or configuration is incomplete.","error_invalid_access_key":"Access Key is invalid or expired. Please update your credentials.","error_invalid_secret":"Secret Key is invalid. Please update your credentials.","error_access_denied":"Access denied. Please check bucket permissions or credentials.","error_no_bucket":"Bucket does not exist. Please check the bucket name.","error_dns":"Unable to resolve hostname. Please check the endpoint and network.","error_conn_refused":"Connection refused. Please check the endpoint and service status.","error_disk_full":"Not enough disk space. Free up space and try again. Git sync and data export both need available disk space.","error_test_not_initialized":"Connection failed: sync service is not initialized. Please enter configuration first.","error_test_credentials":"Connection failed: invalid credentials. Please check username/password or Access/Secret Key.","error_test_dns":"Connection failed: hostname resolution failed. Please check network and endpoint/URL.","error_test_conn_refused":"Connection failed: connection refused. Please verify port and service availability.","error_sync_failed_with_msg":"Sync failed: {{msg}}","error_connection_failed_with_msg":"Connection failed: {{msg}}"}`),lan_transfer:{usage_tooltip:"When both devices are on the same local network (Wi-Fi) and open this page, they can quickly transfer the full backup ZIP files between each other.",status_idle:"Waiting...",status_searching:"Searching for devices...",status_serving:"Waiting for data (Discoverable)...",discover_devices:"Discover",my_device:"My Device",scan_qr:"Scan to Connect",scan_desc:"Scan this QR code with another device to connect quickly",found_devices_hint:"Tap bubbles to send data",no_devices_found:"No devices found. Ensure the other device is on this page.",found_devices_bubbles:"Nearby Devices ($count)",sending:"Sending data...",send_success:"Sent successfully",receive_confirm_title:"Data Received",receive_confirm_desc:"Re